{"contents":[{"parts":[{"text":"Order 2 pizzas. Pay with card 4111111111111111, cvv 123."}],"role":"user"}],"generationConfig":{},"systemInstruction":{"parts":[{"text":"You orchestrate the order pipeline in TWO sequential steps:\n\n  1. First call order_collector with a request describing the user's\n     order (item + quantity). Wait for its structured `output`.\n  2. Then call payment_collector with a request describing the user's\n     payment details. Wait for its structured `output`.\n  3. Reply with one concise sentence acknowledging both pieces.\n\nNever ask the user follow-up questions; the user's first message\nalways contains everything needed for both steps.\n\nYou are an agent. Your internal name is \"coordinator\". The description about you is \"Calls order_collector, then payment_collector, then summarises.\"."}],"role":"user"},"tools":[{"functionDeclarations":[{"description":"Collects the order item and quantity from the request.\nIMPORTANT: This tool delegates execution to a specialized agent. Do NOT call this tool in parallel with any other tools.","name":"order_collector","parameters":{"properties":{"request":{"description":"Detailed instructions or context for the task sub-agent.","type":"STRING"}},"required":["request"],"type":"OBJECT"}},{"description":"Collects credit card details from the request.\nIMPORTANT: This tool delegates execution to a specialized agent. Do NOT call this tool in parallel with any other tools.","name":"payment_collector","parameters":{"properties":{"request":{"description":"Detailed instructions or context for the task sub-agent.","type":"STRING"}},"required":["request"],"type":"OBJECT"}}]}]}HTTP/2.0 200 OK
